{"id":60,"date":"2010-10-06T23:30:00","date_gmt":"2010-10-07T03:30:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/jparrott1908.wordpress.com\/2010\/10\/06\/the-truly-strong-are-those-who-control-themselves-when-angry"},"modified":"2025-06-27T05:20:52","modified_gmt":"2025-06-27T01:20:52","slug":"strong-control-anger","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/10\/06\/strong-control-anger\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Anger: Truly strong control themselves when enraged"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201c<strong>The strongest are not the best wrestlers. Verily, the strongest are those who control themselves when angry.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6114, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2609<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/strong>\u00a0<\/em>(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p>Imam Ibn &#8216;Abdul Barr commented, &#8220;This is evidence that striving against oneself is a more difficult task and is better than striving against the enemy.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Tamhi\u0304d 6\/323<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0647 \u0648\u0633\u0644\u0645 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u062f\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064f \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0635\u064f\u0651\u0631\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u064e\u0651\u062f\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0630\u0650\u064a \u064a\u064e\u0645\u0652\