e upon him, said, \"If a judge makes a ruling, striving to apply his reasoning and he is correct, he will have two rewards. If a judge makes a ruling, striving to apply his reasoning and he is mistaken,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32625,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/03\/allah-mercy-lut-yusuf\/","url_meta":{"origin":60,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Lut: May Allah have mercy on Prophet Lot","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy upon Lot. He had sought refuge in a strong pillar. If I had remained in prison for as long as Joseph, I would have accepted an offer of freedom.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3006,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/22\/jihad-in-way-of-allah-better-world\/","url_meta":{"origin":60,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Striving for Allah is better than the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA single endeavor or journey in the way of Allah is better than everything over which the sun rises and sets.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \u201cIt is better than the world and everything in it.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2810,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/06\/shaytan-anger-seek-refuge\/","url_meta":{"origin":60,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Seek refuge from Satan inciting rage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sulayman ibn Surad reported: Two people insulted each other in the presence of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and the eyes of one of them became red like embers and the veins of his neck were bulging. The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, I know a word\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2057,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/08\/allah-rahmah-prevails-wrath\/","url_meta":{"origin":60,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rahmah: Allah&#8217;s mercy surpasses His wrath","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen Allah completed the creation, He wrote in His book with Him upon the Throne: Verily, My mercy prevails over My wrath.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3194, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2751 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":684,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/08\/prophet-never-said-uff\/","url_meta":{"origin":60,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Manners: The Prophet never even said &#8216;Uff&#8217;","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: I served the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, for ten years. By Allah, he never even said to me, \u201cUff!\u201d He never said harshly, \u201cWhy did you do that?\u201d or, \u201cWhy did you not do that?\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6038, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2309 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/60","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=60"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/60\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuami